%^BOLD%^-=%^BLACK%^Cavern Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The cavern domain focuses upon the secret dark places within the earth. As such, it draws upon stone and darkness, and its spells are strengthened by being in such surroundings in some cases.

Clerics with the Cavern Domain gain the following benefits:
- A +2 sight bonus to see in darkness.
- %^CYAN%^Blindfight%^RESET%^ as a class feat.

The cavern domain contains the following spells:

Stone Throw, Meld Into Stone, Obsidian Flow, Maw Of Stone, Earth Reaver, Wall Of Stone, Stone Body, Earthquake, Clashing Rocks

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: The Faceless One, Seija

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
